1a:T421,Internal evidence describes TiNbN-coated alloy material, while external tier1_manufacturer source explicitly states femoral component is Cobalt-Chromium metal. Material conflict requires resolution: internal claims 'TiNbN Coated Alloy' as base material, external confirms CoCr with TiNbN coating. TiNbN is a surface coating technology, not a base material. External sources confirm Opulent as Meril's total knee system with multiple sub-brands (Gold, Bionik Gold variants mentioned). Internal brochure evidence (18-20 year longevity, hypoallergenic, lowest wear, global sizing) aligns with premium positioning. Entity type confirmed as product_family representing complete TKR system with femoral, tibial, and patellar components. Material specification requires clarification: base material likely CoCr alloy with TiNbN coating applied for enhanced wear resistance and biocompatibility. Send to review to correct material/coating distinction and verify if multiple Opulent variants (Gold, Bionik) should be cataloged separately or as configuration options.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Opulent Knee System","product_name_display":"Opulent Knee System","sku_code":"MRL-ORTHO-003","product_family":"Opulent Knee System","product_family_display":"Opulent Knee System","slug":"opulent-knee-system","images":[{"id":"2b21b1ce0fe0","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfabd/cover_ba12c64c.jpg","original_filename":"cover_OPULENT Gold ST.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":346879,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:03.489153+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"Opulent Knee System | Meril Knee Implants - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Premium TKR with advanced TiNbN coating for greater strength and longevity (18-20 years). Global sizing matrix, hypoallergenic, and lowest wear rate.","pack_size":"","size_variables":[],"create